    "name": "闲置水族馆",
    "steam_appid": 3176710,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176710/extras/752053a23dec376a7397bcf244c94054.avif?t=1741755164\" width=800 height=374 /></span>休闲养鱼模拟游戏《闲置水族馆》显示在您屏幕的便于，可以让您一边工作，一边享受做个养鱼佬的快乐。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176710/extras/390163fbe22bdd5d536618778798db0f.poster.avif?t=1741755164\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176710/extras/390163fbe22bdd5d536618778798db0f.webm?t=1741755164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176710/extras/390163fbe22bdd5d536618778798db0f.mp4?t=1741755164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>为你的小鱼喂食：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >投喂您的小鱼，和您的小鱼结交朋友，解锁新的种类，甚至一些非常稀有的品种</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>装饰你的鱼缸：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >装饰您的鱼缸，把您的桌面装饰成您喜爱的样子，提供了各种装饰物。可以满足您的各种需求，草缸，南美缸，您想要的风格都可以有</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176710/extras/e704241c0396a8ca5a239d8dd6965bd0.poster.avif?t=1741755164\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176710/extras/e704241c0396a8ca5a239d8dd6965bd0.webm?t=1741755164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176710/extras/e704241c0396a8ca5a239d8dd6965bd0.mp4?t=1741755164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多任务并行：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以舒适地放置在屏幕底部，让您在照料小鱼的同时还能完成其他任务。或者开启“专注模式”，安静的欣赏它们，而不用过多的操作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176710/extras/59534be41c68e205f68d0ecdbfbc1974.poster.avif?t=1741755164\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176710/extras/59534be41c68e205f68d0ecdbfbc1974.webm?t=1741755164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176710/extras/59534be41c68e205f68d0ecdbfbc1974.mp4?t=1741755164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挂机获得Steam物品：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着你的游戏时长增加，有机会掉落Steam物品，也许会有意外惊喜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176710/extras/bd9c85b57ffdc1e21fae3ad899c7044d.avif?t=1741755164\" width=792 height=286 /></span></p>",
